findings.title: Excessive use of digits can be avoided
findings.description: The code has a large number of digits that makes it difficult to review and reduces the readability of the code.

findings.title: Unlocked Pragma statements found in the contracts
findings.description: The contracts included unlocked pragma solidity version statements which might lead to accidental deployment to a version with unfixed bugs.

findings.title: Admin/Owner Privileges can be misused either intentionally or unintentionally
findings.description: The contract's admin/owner privileges can be exploited intentionally or unintentionally.
